summary_one_paragraph: On November 19, 1968, Special Agent Alphonso E. Marshall submitted a report regarding attempts to locate Juanita Reyes, a listed character reference for Manuel Marti, born in San Juan, Puerto Rico. Attempts to contact Reyes at two different addresses in New York were unsuccessful; at the first address, she was unknown, and at the second, a relative stated that she had moved back to Puerto Rico over a year prior and had never resided at the previously listed Ogden Avenue address. A courtesy letter was left at one residence, but Reyes did not respond.
title: Agent Report Regarding Manuel Marti Character Reference
